sequenceDiagram
  participant User as Användare
  participant Client as Konfidentiell Klient (t.ex. Webbserver)
  participant AuthorizationServer as Auktoriseringsserver
  participant ResourceServer as Resursserver

  User ->> Client: Initierar Autentisering
  Client ->> AuthorizationServer: POST /registration
  AuthorizationServer -->> Client: { "client_id": "klient-id-här", "client_secret": "klient-hemlighet-här" }

  Client ->> User: Presenterar Klient ID för Godkännande
  User -->> Client: Godkänner Klient

  Client ->> AuthorizationServer: POST /token med klient-id, klient-hemlighet, grant_type, osv.
  AuthorizationServer -->> Client: { "access_token": "åtkomsttoken-här", "token_type": "bearer", "expires_in": 3600 }

  Client ->> ResourceServer: GET /skyddad-resurs med Authorization Header (Bearer åtkomsttoken-här)
  ResourceServer -->> Client: 200 OK (Skyddad Resurs)
